Beautiful place but rubbish everywhere
Aug 2016 ‚Ä¢ Couples
I didn't go in the water as you can see there's garbage floating pretty much everywhere. I didn't wanted to stay in the boat for 3 days so what we did is to check at cat ba island and did a full day tour instead. The cost is almost the same if you take the 3 days tour but I just didn't wanted to not have option about the food and I easily get motion sickness also so staying at cat ba was much better for me. We toured at Lan ha bay and monkey island and some kayaking. For the kayaking be careful, make sure your kayak is good. We passed by some guys and their kayak was broken so they had to swim back to our boat.
