The Pollution of Halong Bay
Apr 2016 ‚Ä¢ Couples
We were really looking forward to our two night cruise on Halong Bay and it did not disappoint. What was sooo disappointing and disgusting to see was the pollution. Debris floating everywhere in the water and each day hundreds of tourist boats releasing their raw sewerage into the Bay. The boat we were on was only four years old and it too dumped its waste into the Bay. Something needs to be done to improve this situation.
